      "updated": 1770620143428,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "I know this is not going to scale, but i will start with a \nnaive solutions and then solve the scaling problems separately",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "I know this is not going to scale, but i will start with a \nnaive solutions and then solve the scaling problems separately",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "EXCMMDlx6DcRDy_-6Oyt-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2807.7542738395077,
      "y": 1545.339079899944,
      "width": 538.11962890625,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3k",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1132095295,
      "version": 259,
      "versionNonce": 982693983,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770626491267,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Whatsapp\n\nFR:\n1. group chat with multiple participants\n2. send receive msgs\n3. users should be able to receive msgs even when they\narent online\n4. send/receive media in msgs",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Whatsapp\n\nFR:\n1. group chat with multiple participants\n2. send receive msgs\n3. users should be able to receive msgs even when they\narent online\n4. send/receive media in msgs",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GKQ2uoBoMpieGhW1Ro8Oc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2093.332127386134,
      "y": 1593.8817959071157,
      "width": 524.6397705078125,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3l",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1891135697,
      "version": 302,
      "versionNonce": 263424721,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770627020912,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "NFR:\n1. low latency for sending/receiving msgs\n2. guaranteed delivery of msgs\n3. handle billion of users with high throughput\n4. msgs should not be stored for longer than required\nin the centralized server\n5. should be resilient against failures",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "NFR:\n1. low latency for sending/receiving msgs\n2. guaranteed delivery of msgs\n3. handle billion of users with high throughput\n4. msgs should not be stored for longer than required\nin the centralized server\n5. should be resilient against failures",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
