      "text": "Social Media Systems related questions have a lot of things to learn about, and it becomes a logical point to group them\nthat way. It will help with the pattern recognition better.\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Social Media Systems related questions have a lot of things to learn about, and it becomes a logical point to group them\nthat way. It will help with the pattern recognition better.\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
